      "role": "user",
      "content": "exactly. it's like the itinerary was written for someone who actually wanted to see things, but i'm just going through the motions. i look at the maps and the routes and i just see lines connecting points that don't matter. i'm just so tired of the transit. i feel like i've reached the final terminal, and i'm just waiting for the gates to close so i don't have to travel anymore. does that make sense? like, is it okay to just want the trip to be over?",
